chez vous.

590
00:41:06,376 --> 00:41:09,038
Comme Smith... ou Anderson.

591
00:41:27,953 --> 00:41:29,328
Puis Carla

592
00:41:29,359 --> 00:41:30,883
a eu le culot de me dire

593
00:41:31,019 --> 00:41:32,581
